The paper studies a problem related to collaborative search, which is a topic in multi-agent systems (MAS) and distributed computing (DC). Therefore, cs.MA and cs.DC are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the application of the results to complex biological systems, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
